title: Removed mandatory "name" field, fixed a longstanding bug where all
message:
Removed mandatory "name" field, fixed a longstanding bug where all
forms would show "form name" in the header. Fixed form submission so
that it uses whichever field has "3" in fldStatus as the name.
Added more to the map, it now has names. This happens to be a build
compatible with iOS 7 as well. No tweaks were necessary. Also made a
couple changes making the app more fluid and quick.
A couple bug fixes, the primary new change is the addition of login
tokens to make the app generally more secure. Warning, this is not too
helpful since the server doesn't have SSL enabled! Passwords are being
sent in cleartext.
